        "management": "Pediatric-inspired protocols (induction, consolidation, maintenance). Berlin-Frankfurt-Munster (BFM) regimen. Tyrosine kinase inhibitors if Ph+. CAR-T (tisagenlecleucel) for relapsed/refractory B-ALL."
